    "body": " - would need to add a storage column and index for orphaned blocks\n   - potentially an index by parent root as well as proposer slot\n - StoreTransactionUpdatesFactory would write orphaned blocks prior to pruning them from data structures.\n\n - alter historical fetch to fetch orphaned blocks?\n\n - potentially implement `/eth/v1/beacon/headers` by parent_root parameter, which would be complicated as no index exists currently for existing blocks, but the value is reduced if only supporting orphaned blocks.\n\nwithout a parent_root index, the only way to tell its orphaned is to get headers from the following slot and see if any of those blocks have this parent...\n\nestimates:\n - storage - 3d\n - api - 5d\n\nso looking at maybe 1 sprint worth of work as a rough estimate.",
